name: TheOfficeQuoteGame
0:
”Alexa, open office quote game”
”Alexa, launch office quote game”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: office quote game
des: Test your knowledge of The Office by trying to guess the name of the character that originally says the quote. Try it out and see how many quotes you can guess correctly. If you guess wrong, Alexa will tell you who that quote belongs to and the game will end. To end the game, simply reply "stop".
